OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,FDementia Jersey has announced a new
OL,7,Fstrategy to avoid the disease after
OL,8,Fnew figures revealed 45% of cases
OL,9,Fcould be avoided.
OL,11,FThe campaign, 'Boost Your Brain', aims
OL,12,Fto encourage islanders to make small
OL,13,Flifestyle changes such as exercising
OL,14,Fthe mind and body and staying socially
OL,15,Fconnected.
