OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,FDementia is the fastest-growing
OL,7,Fdisease affecting those over 65 in
OL,8,FJersey with around 1,600 people
OL,9,Fsuffering - but the charity hopes to
OL,10,Fbeat the myth that dementia is an
OL,11,Finevitable part of growing old.
OL,13,FThe three areas of focus for the
OL,14,Fcampaign are 'Love your Heart, 'Stay
OL,15,FSharp', and 'Keep Connected'.
OL,17,F'Love your heart' aims to get
OL,18,Fislanders to focus on being physically
OL,19,Factive, eating healthily, and not
OL,20,Fsmoking.
