OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,F'Stay Sharp' is a reminder to
OL,7,Fregularly challenge the brain which
OL,8,Fcan help protect it through ageing. It
OL,9,Fpromotes learning a language or
OL,10,Fregularly completing brain training
OL,11,Fexercises.
OL,13,F'Keep Connected' focuses on the
OL,14,Fbeneficial effect of participating in
OL,15,Fgroup activities and volunteering.
OL,16,FDementia Jersey gives examples such as
OL,17,Fhaving a coffee with friends, and says
OL,18,Fany social contact is good for our
OL,19,Fbrains.
