OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,FClaudine Snape, Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer of Dementia Jersey, says:
OL,8,F"This is the biggest campaign we've
OL,9,Fever run, but it's such an important
OL,10,Fmessage that it's possible to reduce
OL,11,Fyour risk of dementia that we need to
OL,12,Fthink big.
OL,14,F"That's one of the reasons we're so
OL,15,Fpleased to be partnering with Public
OL,16,FHealth on this campaign."
