OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,FProfessor Peter Bradley, Director of
OL,7,FPublic Health, says: "Prevention is
OL,8,Fone of the priorities that underpins
OL,9,Fmuch of our work and I'm delighted to
OL,10,Fsee Dementia Jersey lead this campaign
OL,11,Fwhich has prevention at its core.
OL,13,F"The campaign's focus is on
OL,14,Fencouraging islanders to make simple
OL,15,Fchanges now, to dramatically reduce
OL,16,Ftheir risk of Dementia in the future.
